title: Police Officer
subTitle: Jai, a kind-hearted policeman gets killed during one of his encounters. His twin, who is an infamous conman, decides to track down Jai's murderer.

title: Socha Na Tha
subTitle: Initially rejecting an arranged match, Viren and Aditi become friends. However, their growing bond unexpectedly blossoms into love.

title: Insaaf: The Final Justice
subTitle: When a witness is killed, a truthful police officer embarks on a mission to catch the culprit and uncovers a terrifying truth.

title: Sahibaan
subTitle: After being rejected by Sahibaan, Vijay, a philanderer, learns about her love affair with Gopi, a labourer. Soon, a distressed Vijay decides to kill Gopi.

title: Dosti Dushmani
subTitle: Sandeep, Ranjit and Prakash are best friends from childhood. A misunderstanding between Ranjit and Sandeep leads the former to believe that the latter is a criminal.

title: Jis Desh Mein Ganga Rehta Hai
subTitle: Ganga, an innocent man, is raised by a foster couple in a village. When he is brought back to his family in the city, he struggles to fit into modern society.

title: Aarzoo
subTitle: After her fiance, Vijay is killed in a crash, a pregnant Pooja agrees to marry Amar, her childhood friend. However, her life takes yet another turn when Vijay returns to her life.

title: Coolie
subTitle: Zafar's obsessive love for Salma leads to her separation from her son, Iqbal. Twenty years later, Iqbal strives to reunite with his mother.

title: Laadla
subTitle: Raju, an upright union leader, can do anything at his wheelchair-bound mother's behest, even if it means breaking his own heart and giving in to a rude heiress.

title: Ghayal Once Again
subTitle: The lionhearted Ajay Mehra once again takes up the mantle of justice in a troubled society where the powerful believe they can get away with any crime.

title: Gunehgar
subTitle: Ajay Thakur, a police inspector, decides to apprehend the terrorists who plan to usurp Kashmir from India. However, things become complicated when his sister falls in love with one of them.

title: Phone Bhoot
subTitle: Inspired by stories from their childhood, two young men create a business around capturing ghosts. However, their endeavour turns dangerous when they must fulfil their promise to a poltergeist.

title: Kasoor
subTitle: When Shekhar is accused of killing his wife, he hires Simran, a lawyer with a spotless record. She believes he is innocent and starts developing feelings for him, unaware of his true intentions.

title: Lal Baadshah
subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.

title: Kurukshetra
subTitle: ACP Prithviraj, an honest man, arrests Chief Minister Baburao's son for raping a woman. Consequently, Baburao leaves no stone unturned to get revenge against Prithviraj.

title: Maine Pyar Kiya
subTitle: Prem and Suman fall in love with each other, only to be torn apart by family differences. However, Suman's father is willing to give Prem one last chance where he must prove himself worthy of Suman.

title: Gambler
subTitle: Though Inspector Dayashanker is lazy, he unwittingly unearths a criminal conspiracy and becomes the pride of his division overnight. However, a local gangsters turn his life into a nightmare.

title: Jaal: The Trap
subTitle: Ajay, a commando, is forced to kidnap Anita, the home minister's daughter, to free his girlfriend Neha from the clutches of terrorists. In the process, he uncovers a shocking revelation.

title: Race 3
subTitle: The thirst for power drives a wealthy family to become rivals in a risky heist. As a consequence, they face betrayal and danger along the way.

title: Race 3
subTitle: The thirst for power drives a wealthy family to become rivals in a risky heist. As a consequence, they face betrayal and danger along the way.

title: Taaqat
subTitle: Two gangsters working for politicians from opposite parties believe that their respective leaders will provide a better future. The two are pitted against each other when the politicians unite.

title: Ru-Ba-Ru
subTitle: Tara and Nikhil are in a relationship and the former wants to take their relationship to the next step. However, Nikhil's work ambitions poses challenges for them.

title: Khuda Kasam
subTitle: CBI Officer Neetu Singh is framed for the assassination of a chief minister. She then attempts to solve this murder mystery with the help of a man, who is imprisoned for a crime he never committed.

title: Mere Sajna Saath Nibhana
subTitle: Kanhaiya, a poor street performer, falls in love with Chanchal, a wealthy woman. He convinces his mother to ask for her hand in marriage, but things take a turn when Chanchal's father insults her.

title: Dil Ka Kya Kasoor
subTitle: A rich girl, Shalini, falls in love with an orphan, Arun, after he performs the poems she wrote using a pen name. However, things take a tragic turn when Arun marries the principal's daughter, Meena.

title: Haan Maine Bhi Pyaar Kiya
subTitle: Pooja divorces her husband for being unfaithful and gets a job as secretary to a film star. The two fall in love, before her ex-husband returns and she finds herself confused between the two men.

title: Janta Ki Adalat
subTitle: DSP Jyoti foils the plans of Shankar, a prisoner who threatens to kill a minister. But she lends her support to Shankar after she hears about the minister's dark secrets and ill intentions.

title: Chori Chori Chupke Chupke
subTitle: Raj and Priya, a married couple, hire Madhubala, a prostitute, as the surrogate mother of their child. Trouble brews when Madhubala falls in love with Raj and insists on keeping the child.

title: Apna Sapna Money Money
subTitle: Arjun and Shivani are in love, but Shivani's father will never let them marry each other. Later chaos ensues when Arjun enlists the help of his conman cousin, Kishan, to unite him with Shivani.
